<plot>Joe McDoakes is employed as the seventh vice-president in a firm that only makes promotions from the employee ranks. The sixth vice-president tries to tutor Joe in how to get ahead with the boss, but all his ideas backfire. Thrity years later, Joe is the only vice-president left to be promoted but, just as the prized promotion is about to be bestowed, the Boss, as usual, forgets Joe's name...and so does Joe.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503861</url></doc>
